videos.description: Stephen Louis goes up for a 33-yard reception from Ryan Finley, bobbles it but brings it down and stays in bounds for a big gain.
videos.headline: Louis makes a bobbling catch for NC State

videos.description: De'Lance Turner gets Alcorn State into the red zone with a nice 29-yard run up the sideline.
videos.headline: Turner sets up Alcorn State with a big run

videos.description: Kelvin Harmon gets ahead of his man on a 48-yard touchdown from Ryan Finley for NC State's first score.
videos.headline: Finley connects with Harmon on a big TD

videos.description: Lamar Jackson throws his first touchdown of the game on a 23-yard pass to Seth Dawkins who bobbles it but manages to hold on.
videos.headline: Dawkins holds on for Louisville TD

videos.description: NC State's Ryan Finley finds Jaylen Samuels for a short catch that he turns into a 79-yard reception.
videos.headline: Samuels turns short catch into huge run

videos.description: Stephen Louis beats his man and jumps for a 39-yard reception from Ryan Finley, moving NC State into the red zone.
videos.headline: Louis leaps for 39-yard catch

videos.description: Nyheim Hines takes it in quickly from 11 yards out after a big catch for NC State to increase its lead to 17-7.
videos.headline: Hines scores on the ground for NC State

videos.description: Nyheim Hines goes for a 45-yard run to get NC State into the red zone late in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Hines breaks out for 45 yards

videos.description: Nyheim Hynes runs in a 7-yard touchdown for his second of the game for NC State.
videos.headline: Hines rushes for his 2nd TD

videos.description: Lamar Jackson makes his own way to the end zone after feeling the pressure to score a 4-yard rushing touchdown for Louisville.
videos.headline: Jackson scrambles for a TD

videos.description: Reggie Gallaspy II converts a three-yard rushing touchdown after a big pass play and completes the two-point conversion.
videos.headline: Gallaspy pads NC State lead with rushing TD

videos.description: Lamar Jackson finds Seth Dawkins in stride who runs 65 yards before being tackled in the red zone.
videos.headline: Dawkins' big gain gets Louisville in the red zone

videos.description: Lamar Jackson takes it in from three yards out late in the 4th quarter, however Lousiville would miss the PAT, keeping the score 32-25 NC State.
videos.headline: Jackson rushes for his 2nd TD

videos.description: Lamar Jackson's pass is tipped and intercepted by Germaine Pratt and returned 25 yards for a touchdown late in the 4th quarter.
videos.headline: Jackson throws pick-six

videos.description: NC State head coach Dave Doeren says he couldn't be more proud of his team after a hard-fought win against Louisville.
videos.headline: Doeren emotional after win

videos.description: Dave Flemming, Matt and Tim Hasselbeck discuss the play of Ryan Finley and Lamar Jackson after NC State's 39-25 win over Louisville.
videos.headline: Finley and Jackson put on a show in Raleigh
